<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">General distribution: Southern Europe</emphasis>
: Albania, Bulgaria, Croatia (
<bibRefCitation author="Novak, P" journalOrPublisher="Godisnjak Bioloskog Instituta Univerziteta u Sarajevu" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="31 - 53" refId="B5743341" refString="Novak, P, Wagner, Wilhelm, 1962. Prilog poznavanju faune Homoptera Dalmacije. Godisnjak Bioloskog Instituta Univerziteta u Sarajevu 15: 31 - 53" title="Prilog poznavanju faune Homoptera Dalmacije" volume="15" year="1962">Novak and Wagner 1962</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Schedl, Wolfgang" journalOrPublisher="Zoologische Jahrbuecher, Jena" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="1 - 27" refId="B5743561" refString="Schedl, Wolfgang, 1986. Zur Verbreitung, Biologie und Oekologie der Singzikaden von Istrien und dem angrenzenden Kuestenland (Homoptera: Cicadidae and Tibicinidae). Zoologische Jahrbuecher, Jena 113 (1): 1 - 27" title="Zur Verbreitung, Biologie und Oekologie der Singzikaden von Istrien und dem angrenzenden Kuestenland (Homoptera: Cicadidae and Tibicinidae)" volume="113" year="1986">Schedl 1986</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Joermann, G" journalOrPublisher="Zoologischer Anzeiger" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="283 - 296" refId="B5743140" refString="Joermann, G, Schneider, H, 1987. The songs of four species of cicada in Yugoslavia (Homoptera: Cicadidae). Zoologischer Anzeiger 219 (5/6): 283 - 296" title="The songs of four species of cicada in Yugoslavia (Homoptera: Cicadidae)" volume="219" year="1987">Joermann and Schneider 1987</bibRefCitation>
), France, Greece, Italy (including Sicily), Montenegro (Trilar &amp; Gogala, unpublished data), North Macedonia, Portugal, Romania, Serbia (
<bibRefCitation author="Petrik, A." journalOrPublisher="Rad Vojvođanskih Muzeja" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="87 - 113" refId="B5743371" refString="Petrik, A., 1958. Entomofauna Deliblatske pescare. Rad Vojvođanskih Muzeja 7: 87 - 113" title="Entomofauna Deliblatske pescare" volume="7" year="1958">Petrik 1958</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Jankovic, Ljubodrag" journalOrPublisher="Srpska Akademija Nauka i Umetnosti, Zlbornik Radova o Enbomofauni SR Srbije" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="85 - 112" refId="B5743130" refString="Jankovic, Ljubodrag, 1975. Fauna Homoptera: Auchenorrhyncha SR Srbije. Srpska Akademija Nauka i Umetnosti, Zlbornik Radova o Enbomofauni SR Srbije 1: 85 - 112" title="Fauna Homoptera: Auchenorrhyncha SR Srbije" volume="1" year="1975">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Janković">Jankovic</normalizedToken>
1975
</bibRefCitation>
), Slovenia, Spain; 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Central Europe</emphasis>
: Austria, Hungary, Poland, Slovakia, Switzerland; 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Eastern Europe</emphasis>
: Russia (South European Russia), Ukraine; 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Middle East</emphasis>
: Iran; 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Transcaucasia</emphasis>
: Armenia, Azerbaijan, Georgia (all data except for the countries with the citation in brackets are summarised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Duffels, J P" journalOrPublisher="Dr W Junk Publisher, Dordrecht, Boston, Lancaster" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5742783" refString="Duffels, J P, van der Laan, P A, 1985. Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Homoptera, Auchenorhyncha) 1956-1980. Dr W Junk Publisher, Dordrecht, Boston, Lancaster" title="Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Homoptera, Auchenorhyncha) 1956 - 1980" year="1985">Duffels and van der Laan 1985</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Sanborn, Allen F" journalOrPublisher="Academic Press / Elsevier, London, UK" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743532" refString="Sanborn, Allen F, 2014. Catalogue of the Cicadoidea. Academic Press/Elsevier, London, UK" title="Catalogue of the Cicadoidea" year="2014">Sanborn 2014</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
There is a doubtful citation of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Scopoli" baseAuthorityYear="1763" genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes plebejus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="plebejus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Lyristes plebejus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for Germany (
<bibRefCitation author="Nast, Janusz" journalOrPublisher="Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743322" refString="Nast, Janusz, 1972. Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list. Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" title="Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list" year="1972">Nast 1972</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wolf, H" journalOrPublisher="Heimatjb. Dillkreis" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="30 - 39" refId="B6075842" refString="Wolf, H, 1974. Aus der Insektenwelt des Dillkreis. Heimatjb. Dillkreis 17: 30 - 39" title="Aus der Insektenwelt des Dillkreis" volume="17" year="1974">Wolf 1974</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nast, Janusz" journalOrPublisher="Annales Zoologici" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="536 - 661" refId="B5743312" refString="Nast, Janusz, 1987. The Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) of Europe. Annales Zoologici 40 (15): 536 - 661" title="The Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) of Europe" volume="40" year="1987">Nast 1987</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Lodos, Niyazi" journalOrPublisher="Tuerkiye Bitki Koruma Dergisi" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="67 - 82" refId="B5743208" refString="Lodos, Niyazi, Kalkandelen, Ayla, 1981. Preliminary list of Auchenorrhyncha with notes on distribution and importance of species in Turkey. V. Families Flalidae, Ricaniidae and Cicadidae. Tuerkiye Bitki Koruma Dergisi 5 (2): 67 - 82" title="Preliminary list of Auchenorrhyncha with notes on distribution and importance of species in Turkey. V. Families Flalidae, Ricaniidae and Cicadidae" volume="5" year="1981">Lodos and Kalkandelen 1981</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Quartau, Jose Alberto" journalOrPublisher="Rapport WWF, Marseille" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="367 - 375" refId="B5743489" refString="Quartau, Jose Alberto, Fonseca, P J, 1988. An annotated check-list of the species of cicadas known to occur in Portugal (Homoptera: Cicadoidea). In: Proceedings of the 6th Auchenorrhyncha Meeting, Turin, Italy 7-11 September 1987.: 367 - 375" title="An annotated check-list of the species of cicadas known to occur in Portugal (Homoptera: Cicadoidea)" volumeTitle="Proceedings of the 6 th Auchenorrhyncha Meeting, Turin, Italy 7 - 11 September 1987." year="1988">Quartau and Fonseca 1988</bibRefCitation>
), as it is not listed in the latest overview of fauna (
<bibRefCitation author="Nickel, H" journalOrPublisher="Rote Liste gefaehrdeter Tiere, Pflanzen und Pilze Deutschlands, Band 4: Wirbellose Tiere (Teil 2)" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B6075803" refString="Nickel, H, Achtziger, R, Biedermann, R, Bueckle, C, Deutschmann, U, Niedringhaus, R, Remane, R, Walter, S, Witsack, W, 2016. . Rote Liste gefaehrdeter Tiere, Pflanzen und Pilze Deutschlands, Band 4: Wirbellose Tiere (Teil 2) 70 (4)" volume="70 (4)" year="2016">Nickel et al. 2016</bibRefCitation>
). There are also doubtful records for Corsica (
<bibRefCitation author="Servadei, A" journalOrPublisher="Calderini, Bologna" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743610" refString="Servadei, A, 1967. Rhynchota (Heteroptera, Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Catalogo topografico e sinonimico. - Fauna d'Italia, Vol. IX. Calderini, Bologna" title="Rhynchota (Heteroptera, Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Catalogo topografico e sinonimico. - Fauna d'Italia, Vol. IX" year="1967">Servadei 1967</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nast, Janusz" journalOrPublisher="Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743322" refString="Nast, Janusz, 1972. Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list. Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" title="Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list" year="1972">Nast 1972</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, Michel" journalOrPublisher="Travaux du Laboratoire Biologie et Evolution des Insectes Hemipteroidea, Ecole Pratique des Hautes Etudes, Biologie et Evolution des Insectes" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="55 - 86" refId="B5742690" refString="Boulard, Michel, 1992. Identite et bio-ecologie de Cicadatra atra (Olivier, 1790), la cigale noire, in Gallia primordia patria (Homoptera, Cicadoidea, Cicadidae). Travaux du Laboratoire Biologie et Evolution des Insectes Hemipteroidea, Ecole Pratique des Hautes Etudes, Biologie et Evolution des Insectes 5: 55 - 86" title="Identite et bio-ecologie de Cicadatra atra (Olivier, 1790), la cigale noire, in Gallia primordia patria (Homoptera, Cicadoidea, Cicadidae)" volume="5" year="1992">Boulard 1992b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Guglielmino, Adalgisa" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Museum fuer Naturkunde im Berlin, Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="161 - 172" refId="B5742995" refString="Guglielmino, Adalgisa, D'Urso, Vera, Alma, Alberto, 2000. Auchenorrhyncha (Insecta, Homoptera) from Sardinia (Italy): A faunistic, ecological and zoogeographical contribution. Mitteilungen aus dem Museum fuer Naturkunde im Berlin, Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 47 (2): 161 - 172" title="Auchenorrhyncha (Insecta, Homoptera) from Sardinia (Italy): A faunistic, ecological and zoogeographical contribution" volume="47" year="2000">Guglielmino et al. 2000</bibRefCitation>
) and Sardinia (
<bibRefCitation author="Servadei, A" journalOrPublisher="Calderini, Bologna" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743610" refString="Servadei, A, 1967. Rhynchota (Heteroptera, Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Catalogo topografico e sinonimico. - Fauna d'Italia, Vol. IX. Calderini, Bologna" title="Rhynchota (Heteroptera, Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Catalogo topografico e sinonimico. - Fauna d'Italia, Vol. IX" year="1967">Servadei 1967</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nast, Janusz" journalOrPublisher="Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743322" refString="Nast, Janusz, 1972. Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list. Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" title="Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list" year="1972">Nast 1972</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, Michel" journalOrPublisher="Travaux du Laboratoire Biologie et Evolution des Insectes Hemipteroidea, Ecole Pratique des Hautes Etudes, Biologie et Evolution des Insectes" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="55 - 86" refId="B5742690" refString="Boulard, Michel, 1992. Identite et bio-ecologie de Cicadatra atra (Olivier, 1790), la cigale noire, in Gallia primordia patria (Homoptera, Cicadoidea, Cicadidae). Travaux du Laboratoire Biologie et Evolution des Insectes Hemipteroidea, Ecole Pratique des Hautes Etudes, Biologie et Evolution des Insectes 5: 55 - 86" title="Identite et bio-ecologie de Cicadatra atra (Olivier, 1790), la cigale noire, in Gallia primordia patria (Homoptera, Cicadoidea, Cicadidae)" volume="5" year="1992">Boulard 1992b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Quartau, Jose Alberto" journalOrPublisher="Rapport WWF, Marseille" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="367 - 375" refId="B5743489" refString="Quartau, Jose Alberto, Fonseca, P J, 1988. An annotated check-list of the species of cicadas known to occur in Portugal (Homoptera: Cicadoidea). In: Proceedings of the 6th Auchenorrhyncha Meeting, Turin, Italy 7-11 September 1987.: 367 - 375" title="An annotated check-list of the species of cicadas known to occur in Portugal (Homoptera: Cicadoidea)" volumeTitle="Proceedings of the 6 th Auchenorrhyncha Meeting, Turin, Italy 7 - 11 September 1987." year="1988">Quartau and Fonseca 1988</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Guglielmino, Adalgisa" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Museum fuer Naturkunde im Berlin, Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="161 - 172" refId="B5742995" refString="Guglielmino, Adalgisa, D'Urso, Vera, Alma, Alberto, 2000. Auchenorrhyncha (Insecta, Homoptera) from Sardinia (Italy): A faunistic, ecological and zoogeographical contribution. Mitteilungen aus dem Museum fuer Naturkunde im Berlin, Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 47 (2): 161 - 172" title="Auchenorrhyncha (Insecta, Homoptera) from Sardinia (Italy): A faunistic, ecological and zoogeographical contribution" volume="47" year="2000">Guglielmino et al. 2000</bibRefCitation>
), as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Scopoli" baseAuthorityYear="1763" genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes plebejus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="plebejus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Lyristes plebejus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was never found in recent fieldwork with bioacoustic methods on these Islands (
<bibRefCitation author="Puissant, Stephane" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe Entomologique de France" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="429 - 436" refId="B5743469" refString="Puissant, Stephane, Sueur, Jerome, 2001. Contribution a l'etude des Cigales de Corse (Hemiptera, Cicadidae). Bulletin de la Societe Entomologique de France 106 (5): 429 - 436" title="Contribution a l'etude des Cigales de Corse (Hemiptera, Cicadidae)" volume="106" year="2001">Puissant and Sueur 2001</bibRefCitation>
; Thomas Hertach, personal communication).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Scopoli" baseAuthorityYear="1763" genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes plebejus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="plebejus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Lyristes plebejus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is on the eastern side of Rechinger's line in the Aegean Sea replaced by 
<taxonomicName genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes gemellus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="gemellus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Lyristes gemellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Boulard, 1988 (
<bibRefCitation author="Simoes, Paula Cristina" journalOrPublisher="Biologia, Section Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="961 - 965" refId="B5743652" refString="Simoes, Paula Cristina, Quartau, Jose Alberto, 2013. Distribution of cicadas of the genus Lyristes (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) in the eastern Mediterranean area. Biologia, Section Zoology 68 (5): 961 - 965" title="Distribution of cicadas of the genus Lyristes (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) in the eastern Mediterranean area" volume="68" year="2013">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Simões">Simoes</normalizedToken>
and Quartau 2013
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Gogala, Matija" journalOrPublisher="Acta Entomologica Slovenica" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="45 - 58" refId="B5742905" refString="Gogala, Matija, Trilar, Tomi, 2014. Distribution of endemic cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) on Evia and adjacent islands in Greece. Acta Entomologica Slovenica 22 (1): 45 - 58" title="Distribution of endemic cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) on Evia and adjacent islands in Greece" volume="22" year="2014">Gogala and Trilar 2014</bibRefCitation>
), which is bioacoustically proven on the east Aegean Islands: Lesbos, Chios, Ikaria, Samos and Rhodes (
<bibRefCitation author="Simoes, Paula Cristina" journalOrPublisher="Biologia, Section Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="961 - 965" refId="B5743652" refString="Simoes, Paula Cristina, Quartau, Jose Alberto, 2013. Distribution of cicadas of the genus Lyristes (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) in the eastern Mediterranean area. Biologia, Section Zoology 68 (5): 961 - 965" title="Distribution of cicadas of the genus Lyristes (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) in the eastern Mediterranean area" volume="68" year="2013">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Simões">Simoes</normalizedToken>
and Quartau 2013
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Gogala, Matija" journalOrPublisher="Acta Entomologica Slovenica" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="45 - 58" refId="B5742905" refString="Gogala, Matija, Trilar, Tomi, 2014. Distribution of endemic cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) on Evia and adjacent islands in Greece. Acta Entomologica Slovenica 22 (1): 45 - 58" title="Distribution of endemic cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) on Evia and adjacent islands in Greece" volume="22" year="2014">Gogala and Trilar 2014</bibRefCitation>
), as well as Kalymnos and Kos (Trilar &amp; Gogala, unpublished data) and further east in Turkey (Provinces of Aydin, Antalya and Mersin) (Trilar &amp; Gogala, unpublished data) and Cyprus (
<bibRefCitation author="Simoes, Paula Cristina" journalOrPublisher="Biologia, Section Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="961 - 965" refId="B5743652" refString="Simoes, Paula Cristina, Quartau, Jose Alberto, 2013. Distribution of cicadas of the genus Lyristes (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) in the eastern Mediterranean area. Biologia, Section Zoology 68 (5): 961 - 965" title="Distribution of cicadas of the genus Lyristes (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) in the eastern Mediterranean area" volume="68" year="2013">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Simões">Simoes</normalizedToken>
and Quartau 2013
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Scopoli" baseAuthorityYear="1763" genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes plebejus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="plebejus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Lyristes plebejus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is also cited in literature for Israel (
<bibRefCitation author="Schedl, Wolfgang" journalOrPublisher="Linzer Biologische Beitraege" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="823 - 837" refId="B5743571" refString="Schedl, Wolfgang, 1999. Contribution to the singing cicadas of Israel and adjacent countries (Homoptera, Auchenorryncha: Cicadidae et Tibicinidae). Linzer Biologische Beitraege 31 (2): 823 - 837" title="Contribution to the singing cicadas of Israel and adjacent countries (Homoptera, Auchenorryncha: Cicadidae et Tibicinidae)" volume="31" year="1999">Schedl 1999</bibRefCitation>
) and Syria (
<bibRefCitation author="Lodos, Niyazi" journalOrPublisher="Tuerkiye Bitki Koruma Dergisi" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="67 - 82" refId="B5743208" refString="Lodos, Niyazi, Kalkandelen, Ayla, 1981. Preliminary list of Auchenorrhyncha with notes on distribution and importance of species in Turkey. V. Families Flalidae, Ricaniidae and Cicadidae. Tuerkiye Bitki Koruma Dergisi 5 (2): 67 - 82" title="Preliminary list of Auchenorrhyncha with notes on distribution and importance of species in Turkey. V. Families Flalidae, Ricaniidae and Cicadidae" volume="5" year="1981">Lodos and Kalkandelen 1981</bibRefCitation>
), but in our opinion, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
<taxonomicName genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes gemellus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="gemellus">Lyristes gemellus</taxonomicName>
should also be distributed here
</emphasis>
, but this assumption needs to be bioacoustically investigated.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Distribution in Bulgaria</emphasis>
: In Bulgaria, data are available for 76 localities (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F5781068" captionText="Figure 9. Map with localities of Lyristes plebejus in Bulgaria. Black - literature data, blue - data from collections, red - bioacoustic data collected in this survey." figureDoi=".figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/406835" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">9</figureCitation>
). In literature, we found the data for Bulgaria in 
<bibRefCitation author="Yoakimov, D" journalOrPublisher="Sbornik za narodni umotvoreniya, nauka i knizhnina [Collection of folklore, science and literature]" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="1 - 34" refId="B5743855" refString="Yoakimov, D, 1909. Po faunata na Hemiptera v Blgariya [On the fauna of Hemiptera of Bulgaria]. Sbornik za narodni umotvoreniya, nauka i knizhnina [Collection of folklore, science and literature] 25 (7): 1 - 34" title="Po faunata na Hemiptera v Blgariya [On the fauna of Hemiptera of Bulgaria]" volume="25" year="1909">Yoakimov (1909)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Sander, Friedrich Wilhelm" journalOrPublisher="Wissenschaftliche Zeitschrift Friedrich-Schiller-Universitaet Jena, Naturwissenschaftliche Reihe" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="585 - 607" refId="B5743541" refString="Sander, Friedrich Wilhelm, 1985. Zur Kanntnis der Entomofauna von Bulgarien - Zikaden (Homoptera - Auchenorrhyncha). Wissenschaftliche Zeitschrift Friedrich-Schiller-Universitaet Jena, Naturwissenschaftliche Reihe 34: 585 - 607" title="Zur Kanntnis der Entomofauna von Bulgarien - Zikaden (Homoptera - Auchenorrhyncha)" volume="34" year="1985">Sander (1985)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Hava, Jiri" journalOrPublisher="Arquivos entomoloxicos" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="137 - 138" refId="B5743015" refString="Hava, Jiri, 2016. Cicadatra persica (Kirkaldy, 1909) new for Bulgaria (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadidae). Arquivos entomoloxicos 16: 137 - 138" title="Cicadatra persica (Kirkaldy, 1909) new for Bulgaria (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadidae)." volume="16" year="2016">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Háva">Hava</normalizedToken>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Bairyamova, Viola Kirilova" journalOrPublisher="Acta Zoologica Bulgarica" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="55 - 56" refId="B5742576" refString="Bairyamova, Viola Kirilova, 1992. Prouchvaniya vrkhu tsikadnata fauna (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha) na Rodopite [Studies on cicade fauna (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha) of the Rhodopes]. Acta Zoologica Bulgarica 44: 55 - 56" title="Prouchvaniya vrkhu tsikadnata fauna (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha) na Rodopite [Studies on cicade fauna (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha) of the Rhodopes]" volume="44" year="1992">Bairyamova (1992)</bibRefCitation>
lists the species for Rhodope Mts. and 
<bibRefCitation author="Nedyalkov, N" journalOrPublisher="Periodichno spisanie na blgarskoto knizhovno druzhestvo (Periodical Journal of the Bulgarian Literary Society)" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="670 - 692" refId="B5743331" refString="Nedyalkov, N, 1908. Treti prinos km entomologichnata fauna na Blgariya [Third contribution to the entomological fauna of Bulgaria]. Periodichno spisanie na blgarskoto knizhovno druzhestvo (Periodical Journal of the Bulgarian Literary Society) 69 (9-10): 670 - 692" title="Treti prinos km entomologichnata fauna na Blgariya [Third contribution to the entomological fauna of Bulgaria]" volume="69" year="1908">Nedyalkov (1908)</bibRefCitation>
for northern and southern Bulgaria, with the remark that it does not occur above the altitude limit of oak distribution. 
<bibRefCitation author="Arabadzhiev, Denyu" journalOrPublisher="Rastitelna Zashchita [Plant Protection]" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="31 - 33" refId="B5742546" refString="Arabadzhiev, Denyu, 1963. Novi vidove tsikadi - nepriyateli na ovoshchnite drveta u nas [New species of cicadas - pests on the fruit trees in our country]. Rastitelna Zashchita [Plant Protection] 10: 31 - 33" title="Novi vidove tsikadi - nepriyateli na ovoshchnite drveta u nas [New species of cicadas - pests on the fruit trees in our country]" volume="10" year="1963">Arabadzhiev (1963)</bibRefCitation>
considers the species as a pest. The species is also listed in overviews by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nast, Janusz" journalOrPublisher="Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" refId="B5743322" refString="Nast, Janusz, 1972. Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list. Polish Scientific Publishers, Warszawa" title="Palaearctic Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera). An annotated check list" year="1972">Nast (1972)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nast, Janusz" journalOrPublisher="Annales Zoologici" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" pagination="536 - 661" refId="B5743312" refString="Nast, Janusz, 1987. The Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) of Europe. Annales Zoologici 40 (15): 536 - 661" title="The Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) of Europe" volume="40" year="1987">Nast (1987)</bibRefCitation>
, but without exact location information for Bulgaria.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
In Bulgaria, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Scopoli" baseAuthorityYear="1763" genus="Lyristes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lyristes plebejus" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424" rank="species" species="plebejus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">Lyristes plebejus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distributed all over the country with the known data in eastern Danubian Plane, northern lowest hills of the Pre-Balkan, eastern Sub-Balkan valleys, Ograzhden-Vlachina Mts., Sandanski-Petrich Middle Struma valley, Pirin Mt., Dabrash-Batak western Rhodope Mts., Prespa-Chernatitsa western Rhodope Mts., Upper Thracian Plain, Tundzha-Burgas Valley, eastern Rhodope Mts., Haskovo Hills Land and Strandzha Mt. (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F5781068" captionText="Figure 9. Map with localities of Lyristes plebejus in Bulgaria. Black - literature data, blue - data from collections, red - bioacoustic data collected in this survey." figureDoi=".figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/406835" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">9</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">
In this survey, the majority of the population was found between sea level and 800 m (93% of the population) (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 10" captionStartId="F5781072" captionText="Figure 10. Altitudinal distribution of Lyristes plebejus. The percentage of the recorded localities is displayed in 200 - metre altitude zones." figureDoi=".figure10" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/443786" pageId="0" pageNumber="54424">10</figureCitation>
). At the highest altitude, the male specimen from the SOFM collection was recorded, which was found in Chepelare by Vl. Nonev (1105 m a.s.l.).
</paragraph>
